<h2>TaggedPlainCorpus file type</h2>

<!-- Short description -->
<p>
The "TaggedPlainCorpus" file type represents a corpus with one sentence per line.
Each sentence is a space-separated sequence of words in surface-form.
Words that are part of an MWE are surrounded by <tt>&lt;mwepart&gt;</tt> tags.
</p>



